{"tid":110280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]京婦帶孫放煙花墮河　兒子村民施救三人溺亡","createTime":"2017-02-06T14:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T13:30:17.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fde62f3489bc374dda37a28c143127ad8bb6967a","tid":110280,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170206/bkncn-20170206203653213-0206_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170206%2Fbkncn-20170206203653213-0206_05011_001.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d7d764a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170206/bkncn-20170206203653213-0206_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n北京懷柔區一名老婦昨晚帶孫兒到河邊放煙花，其間她不慎跌落河中。老婦的兒子和一名村民發現後先後落水救人，卻同告遇溺。最終三人被救上岸時，均已證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n懷柔消防昨晚接報，指湯河口鎮小黃塘村有人遇溺，隨即出動8名消防員趕往現場救援。從老婦孫兒的口中得知，落水者是其祖母和父親，以及一位村民。<br />\n<br />\n孩子表示，當時8時，因家人發生糾紛，祖母帶他到河邊放煙花，隨後父親前來尋找。未料祖母不慎落水，父親發現後即跳水救援，而他便返回村莊求救，途中遇到一名村民，該村民獲悉後趕往救人。孫兒又稱，直到他帶人返回事發現場，三人均已遇溺，並由另一名村民報警。<br />\n<br />\n直至今日凌晨零时20分左右，消防員才將三名遇溺者全部救起。惟在場的醫護人員檢查後，證實三人均已無生命迹象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8e31c1d321cdcc5256254649b9e213791f1229","tid":110280,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59f66a1377ad7c9f1a6760d6b52b5f9413eb68d3","tid":110280,"uid":27024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"個孫真係天煞孤星"},{"pid":"d652b7165dd3f6b30ffdd4515f189cbb918e8c2d","tid":110280,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79bb4addf377ba61d4bd3b6ec1b3802e009fb95","tid":110280,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"d3e9a2b1a950bdb06d5957c9b3eba54750731f72","tid":110280,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"每次見到呢個巴打開post都覺得好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}